## 6. Sweet-spot

{{SWEET_SPOT}}

Ranking is a simple utility `agg_tok_per_s - 0.1 * ttft_p99_ms - 0.02 * vram_mib` that favours high aggregate throughput, tight tails, and low memory pressure. Adjust the weights in render_report.py::pick_sweet_spot if the deployment has different priorities (e.g. TTFT-dominated user UX, larger TTFT penalty).

